g\n| 16 May 2013\n| [http://councilportal.cumbria.gov.uk/mgExecPostDetails.aspx?ID=973 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Derbyshire County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" | \n| Barry Lewis\n| 24 May 2017\n| [https://www.derbyshire.gov.uk/council/council_works/cabinet/cabinet_members/default.asp URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Devon County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" | \n| John Hart\n| 25 June 2009\n| [http://democracy.devon.gov.uk/mgExecPostDetails.aspx?ID=143 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Dorset County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| Rebecca Knox\n| 18 May 2017\n| [http://dorset.moderngov.co.uk/mgExecPostDetails.aspx?ID=241 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[East Sussex County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| Keith Glazier\n| 21 May 2013\n| [https://democracy.eastsussex.gov.uk/mgExecPostDetails.aspx?ID=175 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Essex County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| David Finch\n| 14 May 2013\n| [https://cmis.essexcc.gov.uk/Essexcmis5/Councillors/tabid/62/ctl/ViewCMIS_Person/mid/480/id/126/ScreenMode/Ward/Default.aspx URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Gloucestershire County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| Mark Hawthorne {{Post-nominals|country=UK|MBE}}\n| 19 May 2010\n| [http://glostext.gloucestershire.gov.uk/mgExecPostDetails.aspx?ID=753 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Hampshire County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Roy Perry]]\n| 23 May 2013\n| [http://democracy.hants.gov.uk/mgCommitteeDetails.aspx?ID=134 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Hertfordshire County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| David Williams\n| 21 Novembe