ia/2018-03-15/heather-smith-quits-as-leader-of-northamptonshire-county-council/|accessdate=15 March 2018|publisher=[[ITV News]]|date=15 March 2018}}</ref>\n| [http://www3.northamptonshire.gov.uk/councilservices/council-and-democracy/councillors-and-committees/Pages/cabinet.aspx URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Nottinghamshire County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Kay Cutts]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR|MBE}}\n| 25 May 2017\n| [http://www.nottinghamshire.gov.uk/council-and-democracy/council-structure/council-key-roles URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Oxfordshire County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| Ian Hudspeth\n| 15 May 2012\n| [https://www.oxfordshire.gov.uk/cms/content/leader-council URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Somerset County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| David Fothergill\n| 24 May 2017\n| [http://www.somerset.gov.uk/councillors-and-democracy/cabinet/leader-of-the-council/ URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Staffordshire County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| Philip Atkins {{post-nominals|country=GBR|OBE}}\n| 18 June 2009\n| [https://www.staffordshire.gov.uk/yourcouncil/decisionmakingcouncil/roleofthecabinet/RoleoftheCabinet.aspx URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Suffolk County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| Matthew Hicks\n| 24 May 2018\n| [https://www.suffolk.gov.uk/council-and-democracy/the-council-and-its-committees/cabinet/#tab2 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Surrey County Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[David Hodge (councillor)|David Hodge]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR|CBE}}\n| 11 October 2011\n| [https://mycouncil.surreycc.gov.uk/mgExecPostDetails.aspx?ID=436 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Warwickshire County Council]]\n| Le