ocracy.gateshead.gov.uk/mgExecPostDetails.aspx?ID=197 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Kirklees Council|Kirklees Borough Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| style=\"background-color: {{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| Shabir Pandor\n| 23 May 2018\n| [https://democracy.kirklees.gov.uk/mgExecPostDetails.aspx?ID=184 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Knowsley Metropolitan Borough Council|Knowsley Borough Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| style=\"background-color: {{Labour Co-operative/meta/color}}\" |\n| Andy Moorhead\n| 22 May 2015\n| [http://councillors.knowsley.gov.uk/mgExecPostDetails.aspx?ID=129&StyleType=standard&StyleSize=none URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Leeds City Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| style=\"background-color: {{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Judith Blake]]\n| 21 May 2015\n| [http://democracy.leeds.gov.uk/mgCommitteeDetails.aspx?ID=102 URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Liverpool City Council]]\n| [[Mayor of Liverpool|Mayor]]\n| style=\"background-color: {{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Joe Anderson (politician)|Joe Anderson]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR|OBE}}\n| [[Mayor of Liverpool#2012|3 May 2012]]{{efn|Previously Leader of the council (May 2010 \u2013 May 2012).}}\n| [http://liverpool.gov.uk/mayor/ URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Manchester City Council]]\n| Leader of the Council\n| style=\"background-color: {{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Richard Leese|Sir Richard Leese]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR|CBE}}\n| May 1996\n| [http://www.manchester.gov.uk/info/200033/councillors_democracy_and_elections/3195/the_members_of_the_executive URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[North Tyneside Metropolitan Borough Council|North Tyneside Borough Council]]\n| [[Mayor of North Tyneside|Mayor]]\n| style=\"background-color: {{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Norma Redfearn]] {{post-nominals|country=GBR|CBE}}\n| [[Mayor of North Tyneside#2013|2 May 2013]]\n| [http://my.northtyneside.gov.uk/category/613/about-elected-mayor URL]\n|-\n! scope=row | [[Newcastl